OL,3,CMan who inflicted burns on pug puppy
OL,4,Cgets suspended sentence
OL,6,FA man who injured a pug puppy by
OL,7,Fcausing horrific burns to the animal
OL,8,Fhas been handed a suspended jail
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FThabiso Luzuko Giyo from Chatham,
OL,12,FKent, appeared at Sevenoaks
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on 1 May and
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to offences under the
OL,15,FAnimal Welfare Act.
OL,17,FGiyo was sentenced to 22 weeks in
OL,18,Fprison, suspended for two years.
