OL,3,CMan who inflicted burns on pug puppy
OL,4,Cgets suspended sentence
OL,6,FHe was also ordered to pay #800 in
OL,7,Fcosts and a #154 victim surcharge, and
OL,8,Fwas disqualified from keeping any
OL,9,Fanimals for three years.
OL,11,FCapri the pug was first brought in to
OL,12,Fa vet by her owner with a large
OL,13,Fswelling to the head believed to have
OL,14,Fbeen caused by a trauma.
OL,16,FIn a witness statement the vet said
OL,17,FCapri was "really calm and relaxed
OL,18,Faround females but shrank away and
OL,19,Ftrembled in the presence of a male
OL,20,Fvet".
