OL,6,FCapri was brought in again in
OL,7,FDecember, where she was in "quite a
OL,8,Fstate".
OL,10,FShe had burns over her face and neck
OL,11,Fand her tongue was swollen to three
OL,12,Ftimes its size.
OL,14,FAn investigation was launched by the
OL,15,FRSPCA and in a statement to the court,
OL,16,Fthe inspector Kirsten Ormerod said:
OL,17,F"Capri's owner told me that on 12
OL,18,FDecember she left Capri in the care of
OL,19,Fher flatmate, called Thabiso Giyo,
OL,20,Fbetween approximately 2.30pm to 6.30pm
OL,21,Fwhile she went out shopping.
