OL,6,F"She stated that on her return at
OL,7,F6.30pm Capri had a sore face. She
OL,8,Fstated Giyo had wiped Capri's face
OL,9,Fwith an exfoliating glove but quite
OL,10,Fquickly Capri's face started to swell
OL,11,Fand she was struggling to breathe so
OL,12,Fshe took Capri to the emergency vet.
OL,14,F"She had red, open wounds to her face,
OL,15,Fnose and around her mouth. Her tongue
OL,16,Fappeared very swollen and she was not
OL,17,Fable to close her mouth due to her
OL,18,Fswollen tongue.
