OL,6,F"She was also audibly breathing loudly
OL,7,Fand appeared lame on her back right
OL,8,Fleg and was very reluctant to put
OL,9,Fweight on it."JThe vet's witness
OL,10,Fstatement added: "Nobody was willing
OL,11,Fto tell us what substance Capri had
OL,12,Fbeen burned with - the flatmate said
OL,13,Fhe gave her a bath and used an
OL,14,Fexfoliating glove on her which didn't
OL,15,Fadd up to the severity of the injuries
OL,16,Fshe presented with.
