OL,6,F"While she was under anaesthetic for
OL,7,Fan endoscopy, she was also x-rayed.
OL,8,FThe x-rays showed a fracture of the
OL,9,Fright (leg). The x-rays also showed
OL,10,Fhealed pelvic fractures from older
OL,11,Finjuries."
OL,13,FCapri's owner told Inspector Ormerod
OL,14,Fthat she had reported the incident to
OL,15,Fpolice and had asked Giyo to leave the
OL,16,Fproperty but gave her a contact number
OL,17,Ffor him.
