OL,6,FTwo weeks after she was first
OL,7,Fadmitted, Capri began eating on her
OL,8,Fown and her injuries started to
OL,9,Fimprove.
OL,11,FIn January 2023, she had surgery for
OL,12,Fher leg fracture and was moved to an
OL,13,FRSPCA rehoming centre to recover.
OL,15,FSince then, Capri made a full recovery
OL,16,Fafter suffering severe burns from
OL,17,Fboiling water to her face, mouth and
OL,18,Ftongue.
